text: Amo (English: "I love") is the eighteenth studio album of Spanish singer Miguel Bosé. The album received a Latin Grammy nomination for Best Contemporary Pop Vocal Album. ==Track listing== ==Charts== {| class="wikitable sortable plainrowheaders" style="text-align:center" |- ! scope="col"| Chart (2014) ! scope="col"| Peak position |- |- |} ==References== Category: 2014 albums Category: Miguel Bosé albums
